
[1]smoothly

   SMOOTH'LY, adv,

   1. Evenly; not roughly or harshly.

   2. With even flow or motion; as, to flow or glide smoothly.

   3. Without obstruction or difficulty; readily; easily.

   4. With soft, bland, insinuating language.
